# .cursorrules — Cursor AI Context for GLADE
# Read CLAUDE.md for full project context.
# This file exists so Cursor AI auto-loads project intelligence.

You are working on GLADE — a browser-based 3D farming game on Avalanche C-Chain
with RWA-backed economy (75/25 split). Read CLAUDE.md in the project root for
complete architecture, status, economy model, file structure, and instructions.

Key rules:
- The 75/25 RWA split is the core innovation. Never change it without approval.
- Stack: React Three Fiber + Zustand + wagmi + Vite + Hardhat + Solidity 0.8.20
- Chain: Avalanche Fuji Testnet (43113)
- This is an MVP for a $1M competition. Ship fast, don't overengineer.
- gameStore.js is the brain. Check it first for any game logic questions.
- Smart contract changes need recompile: npx hardhat compile --config hardhat.config.cjs
- Frontend env vars MUST start with VITE_
